narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Recommend to anyone with an interest in learning new languages.
I think Indonesian is a great language to learn. There is a huge imbalance betweeen american speakers and indonesian speakers.
a great learning experience, and way to get to understand other cultures through language
The greatest decision I ever made in my Yale career, hands down.
I would certainly recommend this course to a fellow student. It is a great class and a very interesting way to learn a foreign language.

Excellent class! I've made great strides in my Bahasa Indonesia skills and had a great time to go along with it. Pak Indriyo is the best! He's really helpful, understanding, and unbelievably forgiving. Plus, he manages to help the class really learn a lot and still seem relaxed and fun!
I would definitely recommend the class for anyone who wants to learn more about an interesting and fun language.
